:QUOTE
Consistency beats brilliance. AI helps you show up every single week.

:INFO
AI-Powered Newsletter Workflow
A repeatable AI workflow lets you go from topic idea to polished newsletter in a fraction of the time. The key is breaking the process into discrete steps where AI handles the heavy lifting.

:PATH
Research Phase
Use Perplexity or ChatGPT to scan recent developments on your topic. Generate a brief summary of the three most relevant angles.

:PATH
Draft Phase
Feed your research summary and audience profile into an AI writing tool. Generate a full draft and rewrite for voice.

:PATH
Schedule Phase
Use Beehiiv or ConvertKit scheduling to queue the issue. Set a consistent send day and track open rates over time.

:COUNTER.half
2 Hours
Total time per issue with AI assist
|
:COUNTER.half
4x Issues
More output versus fully manual writing

:CHECKLIST
Newsletter Automation Checklist
[ ] Define audience and topic niche
[ ] Create a reusable research prompt template
[ ] Create a draft generation prompt with voice guide
[ ] Set up editing pass prompt for clarity and brevity
[ ] Connect to email platform via API or Zapier
[ ] Schedule send and monitor analytics

:NOTE
Your voice is the product. Use AI to generate raw material but always rewrite the opening hook and closing CTA yourself. Readers subscribe for your perspective, not generic copy.